pageMetadata.description: The Great Gator Giveaway is an NFT project that is dedicated to giving our investors the quickest return on their investment as possible.  All 10,000 of our Gators have been hand-drawn and designed by our artist to be collectibles for your wallet along with your ticket into the giveaways.
